{"tid":2460802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五歲女童疑遭虐待致死　繼母自辯指訊息提及想殺死女童只為表達憤怒情緒","createTime":"2021-03-25T05:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T07:34:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf40c0cdb7075705ef1a6eca66b290ff72892ef","tid":2460802,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:14:28.000Z","msg":"五歲女童懷疑遭虐待致死，被控謀殺的繼母繼續自辯。<br />\n<br />\n被告由囚車押送至高等法院。繼母讀出多條傳給丈夫即首被告的訊息，提及她想殺死女童被告解釋不是真的想殺死她，只是表達憤怒的情緒、向丈夫發洩和釋放壓力的方法。<br />\n<br />\n代表律師又讀出被告向丈夫發送短訊的內容，提及女童為她製作的生日卡是學校老師教她，親手寫上「媽媽」兩字，因為前一天是被告生日。被告向丈夫表示「她有心已經很好」，被告忍不住以紙巾抹眼淚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=428737\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D428737&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2Fxv3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=0f8fbedc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D428737&h=29580049\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=428737</a>"},{"pid":"1670069d20fce88e1c943d7002f276133ba5a02c","tid":2460802,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7178cd4b9b7721a42a3b6dc83ad8da9c340f4e6","tid":2460802,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:17:55.000Z","msg":"即係承認搵個女童嚟做出氣袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60d9163b0094f64e9f4e06c9d51500f30382a2b","tid":2460802,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被告向丈夫表示「她有心已經很好」，被告忍不住以紙巾抹眼淚。</blockquote><br />\n鱷魚的眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/mous